          Welcome to SparrowHub!
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Repository of automation scripts</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
              SparrowHub is a repository of <a href="https://github.com/melezhik/Sparrow6">Sparrow</a> plugins - small automation utilities written on many languages, but could be
              run as <a href="http://raku.org">Raku</a> functions or command line.
              To start using plugins one needs just to install Sparrow and set up a Sparrow repository:<br>
              <code>$ zef install --/test Sparrow6<br>
                $ export SP6_REPO=http://sparrowhub.io/repo<br>
                $ s6 --index-update<br>
                $ s6 --plg-run $plg_name
              </code>
          </p>
